title: The Buildings of England
additional-notes: This is a British publication. Its contents may still be copyrighted even without renewals or copyright notices, if they meet GATT copyright restoration requirements for works first published outside the US.

The first issue renewal documented here is for the earliest record we have found that specifically mentions this serial. Volumes in the series have distinctive titles, though, so before concluding a volume is in the public domain, search for renewals for the volume under its distinctive title. We have not systematically checked volume titles for this serial.
